p: The Alarmed end of the spectrum had a higher proportion of degree-qualified individuals in both 2011 and 2016, while the Dismissive end had a higher proportion of trade qualified ( Table 5). However, the educational distinctions between the groups were not so clear in 2016. The Concerned group has had a statistically significant increase in degree qualified individuals and the Disengaged group has had a significant increase in both degree and trade qualified individuals.
